{"tid":120205,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"(保險back office)Medical claims officer vs call centre representative","createTime":"2017-02-14T09:28:20.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-14T16:01:03.000Z","uid":27785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f7d2c9d25b34c41237b2eced3501b1c2dedcf7cd","tid":120205,"uid":27785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-14T09:28:20.000Z","msg":"我而家有呢兩份工嘅offer,假設兩份工人工同地點一樣，邊個post嘅發展空間比較大呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有啲人就話專攻一樣會比較好，有啲人就話一開始應該唔好令到自己方向太窄，究竟點樣先岩呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好迷茫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nMedical insurance既前景值唔值得專攻呢，定應該係call center學習唔同既GI?我長遠黎講都係想做claims/underwriter<br />\n<br />\n仲有想問下call centre係咪通常可以準時走，但claims就ot到死？<br />\n<br />\nSorry好似太多問題，但我真係好迷茫，希望做保險back office嘅巴絲解答下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d83b86b12014aa802bdbdf027f053c316229d69","tid":120205,"uid":27785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-14T09:56:32.000Z","msg":"push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5a57006d027bc822ab5003e55701d1d0abb8400","tid":120205,"uid":9230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-14T10:35:24.000Z","msg":"肯定係做claims啦<br />\n<br />\n做call center, 除咗俾人屌同駁線，基本上學唔到咩保險嘅technical skill，你睇唔到隻file，又話唔到事....<br />\n<br />\n但做call CS你想轉行就好容易...."},{"pid":"4a97d63f0178ed2300e84d51a732ca0dda89150b","tid":120205,"uid":35087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-14T11:23:27.000Z","msg":"Call centre會有咩發展空間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5469d82737a94e40542a9a